MONETIZATION EVENTS
PRICING & CHECKOUT
Event Name Description Properties pricing_viewed Pricing page seen source plan_selected Plan chosen plan_name, billing_cycle checkout_started Began checkout plan, value payment_info_entered Payment submitted payment_method purchase_completed Purchase successful plan, value, currency, transaction_id purchase_failed Purchase failed error_reason, plan 
SUBSCRIPTION MANAGEMENT
Event Name Description Properties trial_started Trial began plan, trial_length trial_ended Trial expired plan, converted (bool) subscription_upgraded Plan upgraded from_plan, to_plan, value subscription_downgraded Plan downgraded from_plan, to_plan subscription_cancelled Cancelled plan, reason, tenure subscription_renewed Renewed plan, value billing_updated Payment method changed - 
